title: What is the name of the song that says 'look what you made me do, I'm with somebody new'? - Quora

response.answer_text: Sounds like a Taylor Swift song but it’s a guess— I rarely listen to her music but did, a little, briefly, when my son was a tween, and these lyrics remind me of the ones I sort of remember. Hope this helps!

Sam Smith “Dancing with a Stranger” You know you can just Google the lyric and get the song title, right? I mean - that’s how I did it… Easy Peezy, lemon squeezy! But you’re gonna keep adding questions about song lyrics here on Quora aren’t you… That was rhetorical.
